# New Service on Subdomain

The following is required to launch a new service on a subdomain.

Register a new ACM in AWS.

Save resulting DNS authentication request.

Email "Cabinet Office Digital and Technology Team" requesting the new CNAME.

Create a new Helm chart for you service. A simple example can be found in the Docs deployment [folder](https://github.com/cabinetoffice/national-leadership-centre-deployment/tree/master/docs).

Deploy the helm chart to EKS.